<p><span lang="ko" xml:lang="ko"><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%ED%95%9C%EA%B5%AD%EC%96%B4" class="extiw" title="wikt:한국어">한국어</a></span>, <span lang="ko" xml:lang="ko"><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%EC%A1%B0%EC%84%A0%EB%A7%90" class="extiw" title="wikt:조선말">조선말</a></span><br />
<i>Hangugeo, Chosŏnmal</i></p>
</th>
</tr>
