<p><a name="Phonology" id="Phonology"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Korean_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Phonology">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Phonology</span></h2>
